376
00:36:20,350 --> 00:36:26,010
Everybody knows that Jin Xian was sealed off long ago and has been sleeping for many years.

377
00:36:26,010 --> 00:36:28,960
I have found the method to break the seal.

378
00:36:28,960 --> 00:36:34,380
Only, it needs... a little bit of blood from Pavillion Leader Qin.

379
00:36:40,300 --> 00:36:44,350
Within three days, we'll be able to wake Jin Xian.

380
00:36:46,970 --> 00:36:51,640
