381
00:36:52,320 --> 00:36:58,750
Naturally not. How could I do something that harmed fellow disciples from the Immortal Sects?

382
00:36:58,750 --> 00:37:03,990
Everyone, thinking back to when Jin Xian led all of our Immortal Sects,

383
00:37:03,990 --> 00:37:07,540
